03b82bbeee69b6658abc7611450743f6c67590b1.query:
WITH uid AS (
                SELECT id
                FROM users
                WHERE username = $1
            )
            INSERT INTO 
                default_bags 
            VALUES 
                ( (SELECT id FROM uid), $2 ) 
            ON CONFLICT (user_id) 
                DO UPDATE SET bag_id = $2

            WHERE bags.id = (
                SELECT 
                    b.id
                FROM 
                    bags b

                    default_bags d ON b.id = d.bag_id

                    users u ON d.user_id = u.id

                    u.username = $1
